title: The Unwritten (v01 - v10) (2010 - 2014) (Digital-TPB) (Minutemen
description:
The Unwritten (v01 - v10) (2010 - 2014) (Digital-TPB) (Minutemen-PhD)


Created by Mike Carey and Peter Gross (who previously had a lengthy creative partnership on Lucifer), The Unwritten follows Tom Taylor, a man whose very existence has been tied to a fictional boy wizard through the manipulations of his father.

After this volume concluded with issue #54, this title was relaunched as The Unwritten: Apocalypse, which follows directly from this volume.

Collected Editions

Vol. 1: Tommy Taylor and the Bogus Identity (#1-5)
Vol. 2: Inside Man (#6-12)
Vol. 3: Dead Man's Knock (#13-18)
Vol. 4: Leviathan (#19-24)
Vol. 5: On to Genesis (#25-30)
Vol. 6: Tommy Taylor and the War of Words (#31-35, 31.5-35.5)
Vol. 7: The Wound (#36-41)
Vol. 8: Orpheus In the Underworld (#42-49)
Vol. 9: The Unwritten Fables (#50-54)
Vol.10: The Unwritten Apocalypse (#01-05)
